# Constants Folder Rules

## SSOT Principles
- All constants MUST use `as const` for immutability
- No duplicate exports across files
- Types defined before usage

## Naming Conventions
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (e.g., `HEADER_NAV_ITEMS`)
- Types: PascalCase (e.g., `NavLink`, `PricingTierSlug`)
- Files: kebab-case (e.g., `navigation.ts`, `pricing.ts`)

## Type Usage
- `NavLink` (label): Simple links for footers/breadcrumbs
- `NavItemWithDropdown` (title): Header navigation with dropdowns

## Before Committing
- Run `pnpm build` to verify no breaking changes
- Ensure no hardcoded values exist in components that should be constants
